strings: <se_def>*: We apologize for the above situation, hey, you must enjoy watching it very much.
<se_def>*: Details are unknown, but he is looking for Durmag in the dark ruins.
<se_def>*: Why do we have to follow him? nice question! It's right here...
<se_def>*: We are here to take revenge on our dear God. Golding (famous casino baccarat owner) is dead!
<se_high>*: Oh fool, this will be your biggest secret. No one knew that he no longer existed.
<se_def>*: I mean, ouch! There! Listen you fool!
<se_def>*: He forgot what had happened and it was hard for him to come to his senses for a while. Let's go back now. I doubt it!
